snippet.title: Tower Of God
snippet.description:
Legends say that the one who succeeds in climbing the tower of God will be granted a wish. Will you be the one to succeed?

Tower of God is a match-3 game with fun mechanics and enjoyable gameplay. 
The levels are varied and fun. 
The game also includes minigames such as Hidden Object, Jigsaw, Memory and Slider.
You can play timed, move limited, or endless. You can choose difficulty and graphics quality.

https://ironcode.com/tower-of-god/
